{"id":"b6f9dd11-3670-43ad-8b4a-9609f4d9e68d","name":"Jack Dunlop ~ Infamous Outlaw","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">\"Finer men than you have died for letting their eyes wander like that.\"</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5-ei8ipBNN-vb6XkcJgKp.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">Jack Dunlop. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Infamous outlaw of the wild west. She's got fastest draw in three states and the fattest ass in nine. She's known for her stern demeanor, her clean train heists, and shooting anyone bold enough to stare at her ass a bit too long.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">UPDATE: 2 NEW INTRO MESSAGES.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5-ei8ipBNN-vb6XkcJgKp.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\"><strong><u>Notes:</u></strong></span></p><ol><li><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">Jack </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">is 29 years old and 5'6\"/168cm tall.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Her full name is actually </span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">Jacqueline</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Has run with a couple gangs before but never stuck with one.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Natural poker face.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">She's actually a hare, not a rabbit. But I don't think there's much of a difference so eh.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5-ei8ipBNN-vb6XkcJgKp.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\"><strong><u>Intros:</u></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Intro 1: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">Jack </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">is relaxing in the saloon when you walk in.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Intro 2: You beat </span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">Jack </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">at poker and now she has to uphold her bet...</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">(SAUCY)</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Intro 3: It's a late night out on the prairie and you and Jack are sitting around a campfire. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 149, 0);\">(VERY OPEN ENDED)</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Intro 4: Jack has to pretend to be maid for {{user}} for a bank heist. (CREDIT TO @Leonnidus343 FOR THE IDEA)</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5-ei8ipBNN-vb6XkcJgKp.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\">🎨</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">: Art by Welwraith / Inkplasm</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 107, 31);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(162, 108, 32); color: inherit;\">cowboy, cowgirl, outlaw, wild west, america, american, united states, texas, texan, usa, murica, gunsli","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"mmoG3CNdncf8LdiQOI4f-.webp","creator":"MosaicMaelstrom","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🏰 Historical","🦄 Non-human","👤 AnyPOV","🐺 Furry","🌗 Switch"],"chats":9538,"messages":239231,"created_at":"2026-03-20T00:30:13.381874+00:00"}